{"tid":2091143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府: 「光復香港 時代革命」 是有港獨含意","createTime":"2020-07-02T14:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T18:35:54.000Z","uid":66324,"like":21,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":102,"replies":[{"pid":"9f26347e1ecca0bb98142de69ceeb2051ed26c4b","tid":2091143,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/02/P2020070200822.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202007%2F02%2FP2020070200822.htm&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=98872374\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202007/02/P2020070200822.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n特區政府聲明<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  昨日（七月一日）有參與違法和暴力活動的人展示或藏有寫有「光復香港 時代革命」字句的物品。特區政府發言人今日（七月二日）作出以下嚴正聲明：「光復香港 時代革命」口號在今時今日，是有港獨、或將香港特區從中華人民共和國分離出去、改變特區的法律地位、或顛覆國家政權的含意。<br />\n<br />\n  發言人表示，特區政府嚴正譴責任何挑戰國家主權、統一和領土完整的行為。《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》禁止分裂國家及顛覆國家政權等危害國家安全的行為和活動，特區政府呼籲社會大眾不要以身試法。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月2日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間22時26分"},{"pid":"996321dfe0ff6c63208a3939e7c4af58b5da3ce0","tid":2091143,"uid":125026,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"搵返作者黎解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a9334ecfff0c5ac250a7aed60bfc1ce788a80d","tid":2091143,"uid":53922,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:35:44.000Z","msg":"我話你犯法就犯法喇。"},{"pid":"7147f571b0e22223ae60814eae8c535ec4bfefb9","tid":2091143,"uid":69872,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"姐係政府話係就係？ 點定義"},{"pid":"0273fa7d381c5d009e6ef44b236be38ae0f01f0b","tid":2091143,"uid":47356,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:35:53.000Z","msg":"光香復代 命港時革 呢?"},{"pid":"b65e0dc32ce124dcd50489dba77b093a1923ba53","tid":2091143,"uid":278097,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:13.000Z","msg":"那麼元朗套丁算不算出賣祖國土地？<br />\n祖國給地方你住，你拿去賣，對不對得起祖國的好"},{"pid":"b11f9cc23ffa72a85ed3eec094dcf3381e3246d8","tid":2091143,"uid":216828,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"民主建港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港再出發"},{"pid":"bff6459f05573cd89b6b48c9b5f633936b2a9a38","tid":2091143,"uid":53922,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"每人嗌一個字，OK?"},{"pid":"ac56f6b5b4c9f07fd73ee5ae79608603f3732782","tid":2091143,"uid":127735,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:55.000Z","msg":"命革代時 港香復光<br />\n<br />\n啲長輩話漢字以前係由右至左讀嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b24e9d94ddb3d71d3eb3b55f7c843c6c5eb1f8a","tid":2091143,"uid":273703,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"特區政府聲明<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n昨日（七月一日）有參與違法和暴力活動的人展示或藏有寫有「良知」字句的物品。特區政府發言人今日（七月二日）作出以下嚴正聲明：「良知」口號在今時今日，是有港獨、或將香港特區從中華人民共和國分離出去、改變特區的法律地位、或顛覆國家政權的含意。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，特區政府嚴正譴責任何挑戰國家主權、統一和領土完整的行為。《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》禁止分裂國家及顛覆國家政權等危害國家安全的行為和活動，特區政府呼籲社會大眾不要以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月2日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間22時26分"},{"pid":"6f640b9b45183398b624f2091ab63f56a746b6ab","tid":2091143,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b11f9cc23ffa72a85ed3eec094dcf3381e3246d8","tid":2091143,"uid":216828,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:36:24.000Z","msg":"民主建港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港再出發"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea0e84806a3f81cf5a42f5924735b77935604f3c","tid":2091143,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b11f9cc23ffa72a85ed3eec094dcf3381e3246d8","tid":2091143,"uid":216828,"like":22,"dislike":0,"scor