b3b55f7c843c6c5eb1f8a","tid":2091143,"uid":273703,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T14:37:00.000Z","msg":"特區政府聲明<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n昨日（七月一日）有參與違法和暴力活動的人展示或藏有寫有「良知」字句的物品。特區政府發言人今日（七月二日）作出以下嚴正聲明：「良知」口號在今時今日，是有港獨、或將香港特區從中華人民共和國分離出去、改變特區的法律地位、或顛覆國家政權的含意。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，特區政府嚴正譴責任何挑戰國家主權、統一和領土完整的行為。《中華人民共和國香港特別行政區維護國家安全法》禁止分裂國家及顛覆國家政權等危害國家安全的行為和活動，特區政府呼籲社會大眾不要以身試法。<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2020年7月2日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間22時26分"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:26:07.000Z","msg":"良知已犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c37903e0db88e9d94634de27d83f11d990133c4","tid":2091143,"uid":288152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:27:51.000Z","msg":"光復香腸 時代夾麵"},{"pid":"d58d00e288c8d637e172bd9f7c916319dbe040c4","tid":2091143,"uid":340081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"林病習種 我最有種<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580f0c897603d24234d285c425d53ef029a8e71e","tid":2091143,"uid":161726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:31:26.000Z","msg":"岩呀岩呀<br />\n我覺得香港再出發同光復香港方向一致＇<br />\n再叫香港再出發會唔會有港獨含意<br />\n再出發大聯盟係唔係獨派？"},{"pid":"8b6a14316b42b4b1ac4c3d72648673ad9a29c6f1","tid":2091143,"uid":14404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/3/32/Img837.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F3%2F32%2FImg837.jpg&h=17b8371c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ff7d4531245e1925965cb682eac9cd60e7fb944a","tid":2091143,"uid":34722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T15:34:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老味咁如果我keep 住份報紙有寫依8個字又犯法?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi